# This folder holds INTERNAL BBL master data — the SAP exports (*.txt) plus the
# generated outputs (findings.csv, *_enriched.csv, we_summary.csv, report.html)
# and the API cache (api_cache.json). The repo deploys to a PUBLIC GitHub Pages
# site, so we DENY EVERYTHING here by default and allow only the source files.
#
# This way any new data file — in ANY format (.xlsx, .json, .geojson, .pdf, …) —
# is ignored automatically and can never be committed by accident.
# To track an additional file, add an explicit "!<name>" line below.

*
!.gitignore
!oereb_check.py
!README.md
!RULE-SET.md
!i18n.json
